{"lemma": "حَقَّ", "slug": "حَقَّ", "root": "ح.ق.ق", "root_slug": "ح-ق-ق", "root_link": "/words/roots/ح-ق-ق", "pos": "N", "pos_camel": "noun", "paradigm": [], "frequency_in_corpus": 0, "cross_references": {"qac": {"found": true, "lemma_key": "حَقّ", "root": "حقق", "pos": "N", "occurrence_count": 247}, "wiktextract": {"found": true, "entry_count": 7, "pos_tags": ["adj", "noun", "verb"], "has_etymology": true, "sense_count": 28}, "lanes": {"found": true, "entry_ids": ["n8555"], "search_url": "https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AD%D9%8E%D9%82%D9%8E%D9%91"}}, "translations": {"en": "to be due", "fa": "واجب شدن", "ur": "واجب ہونا", "tr": "gerekli olmak", "id": "menjadi wajib", "bn": "বাধ্য হওয়া", "es": "ser debido", "fr": "être dû", "de": "fällig werden", "ru": "становиться обязательным", "zh": "成为义务"}, "definition": {"source": "wiktextract", "senses": [{"pos": "verb", "gloss": "to be true, to be confirmed"}, {"pos": "verb", "gloss": "to be right, to be correct"}, {"pos": "verb", "gloss": "to be necessary, to be obligatory, to be imperative"}, {"pos": "verb", "gloss": "to be adequate, to be suitable, to be appropriate, to be fitting", "examples": [{"text": "وَلَقَدْ بَعَثْنَا فِي كُلِّ أُمَّةٍ رَّسُولًا أَنِ ٱعْبُدُوٱ ٱللَّهَ وَاجْتَنِبُوٱ الطَّاغُوتَ فَمِنْهُم مَّنْ هَدَى اللَّهُ وَمِنْهُم مَّنْ حَقَّتْ عَلَيْهِ الضَّلَالَةُ فَسِيرُوٱ فِي الْأَرْضِ فَٱنْظُرُوٱ كَيْفَ كَانَ عَاقِبَةُ الْمُكَذِّبِينَ", "english": "And we certainly sent into every nation a messenger [saying] “worship God and avoid the idol”. And among them were those whom God guided, and among them were those upon whom error was deservedly enacted. So proceed through the earth and see how was the end of the deniers."}]}, {"pos": "verb", "gloss": "to be due"}, {"pos": "verb", "gloss": "to ascertain, to make sure"}, {"pos": "verb", "gloss": "to recognize, to identify"}, {"pos": "verb", "gloss": "to be necessary, to be obligatory, to be imperative"}, {"pos": "verb", "gloss": "to be adequate, to be suitable, to be appropriate, to be fitting"}, {"pos": "verb", "gloss": "to be due"}, {"pos": "noun", "gloss": "verbal noun of حُقَّ (ḥuqqa) (form I)", "tags": ["form-of", "noun-from-verb"]}, {"pos": "noun", "gloss": "verbal noun of حَقَّ (ḥaqqa) (form I)", "tags": ["form-of", "noun-from-verb"]}, {"pos": "noun", "gloss": "equity"}, {"pos": "noun", "gloss": "truth"}, {"pos": "noun", "gloss": "correctness, right"}, {"pos": "noun", "gloss": "rightful possession, property"}, {"pos": "noun", "gloss": "right"}, {"pos": "noun", "gloss": "proper manner"}, {"pos": "noun", "gloss": "reality"}, {"pos": "noun", "gloss": "rights, claims, legal claims", "tags": ["in-plural"], "examples": [{"text": "الْحُقُوق (al-ḥuqūq)", "english": "law, jurisprudence"}]}, {"pos": "adj", "gloss": "true, authentic, real"}, {"pos": "adj", "gloss": "right, fair and reasonable"}, {"pos": "adj", "gloss": "valid, sound, correct"}, {"pos": "noun", "gloss": "jar"}, {"pos": "noun", "gloss": "pitcher"}, {"pos": "noun", "gloss": "hollow, cavity"}, {"pos": "noun", "gloss": "socket of a joint"}, {"pos": "noun", "gloss": "plural of حُقَّة (ḥuqqa)", "tags": ["form-of", "plural"]}]}, "etymology": {"source": "wiktextract", "text": "From the root ح ق ق (ḥ q q). Compare Hebrew חוק (ḥóqq, “law”), Classical Syriac ܚܘܩܐ (ḥuqqā, “rule”), Ge'ez ሐቀቀ (ḥäḳäḳä, “to fasten”), Tigrinya ሓቂ (ḥaqqi, “truth”).\nPerhaps related to حَجَّ (ḥajja, “to convince with legal arguments; to make the pilgrimage to Mecca”) and words corresponding to this root in the other Semitic languages.\n\nUsing the root ح ق ق (ḥ q q) via the idea of “fitting” parts."}, "ipa": ["/ħaq.qa/", "/ħuq.qa/", "/ħaqq/", "/ħuqq/"], "lanes_definition": {"source": "lanes", "entries": [{"entry_id": "n8555", "headword_ar": "حَقَّ", "root": "Hq", "body": [{"kind": "text", "text": ", aor."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, Msb, K, &c.) and"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (IDrd, Msb, K,) [the latter irregular,] inf. n."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Haq~apN", "text_ar": "حَقَّةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(K, TA) and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Haq~N", "text_ar": "حَقٌّ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(IDrd, TA) and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "HuquwqN", "text_ar": "حُقُوقٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (TA,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "i. q."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "SaAra Haq~FA", "text_ar": "صَارَ حَقًّا"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[i. e., accord. to the primary meaning of"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Haq~N", "text_ar": "حَقٌّ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", as explained below, on the authority of Er-Rághib,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "It was,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "became, suitable to the requirements of wisdom, justice, right"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "rightness, truth,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "reality"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "fact;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "to the exigencies of the case"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]: (TA:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "it was,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "became, just, proper, right, correct,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "true; authentic, genuine, sound, valid, substantial,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "real; established,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "confirmed, as a truth"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "fact:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "necessitated, necessary, requisite,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "unavoidable; binding, obligatory, incumbent,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "due:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "syn."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "wajaba", "text_ar": "وَجَبَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "; (T, S, Msb, K, &c.;) and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "vabata", "text_ar": "ثَبَتَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": (Msb, TA:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "it was,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "became, a manifest and an indubitable fact"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "event;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "as explained by IDrd in the Jm; (TA;)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "it happened, betided,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "befell, surely, without doubt"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "uncertainty."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(K.) It is said in the Kur xxxvi. 6,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "laqado Haq~a Alqawolu EalaY A^akovarihimo", "text_ar": "لَقَدْ حَقَّ القَوْلُ عَلَى اَكْثَرِهِمْ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", i. e."}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "The saying,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "“ I will assuredly fill Hell with genii and men together, ” [Kur xi. 120 and xxxii. 13,] (Bd,) or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "the sentence"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "of punishment, (Jel,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "hath become necessitated"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "as suitable to the requirements of justice,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "as being just"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "right,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "to take effect upon the greater number of them;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "syn."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "wajaba", "text_ar": "وَجَبَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (Jel, TA,) and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "vabata", "text_ar": "ثَبَتَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (TA.) And this, namely,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "vabata", "text_ar": "ثَبَتَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", is the meaning of the verb in the phrase,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Haq~a Ealayoka AlqaDaA='u", "text_ar": "حَقَّ عَلَيْكَ القَضَا=ءُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "The sentence was,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or, emphatically,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "is, necessitated as suitable to the requirements of justice to take effect upon thee;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "it was,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "is, necessary, just,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "right, that the sentence should take effect upon thee"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (TA.) [In like manner,] one says,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "yaHiq~u Ealayoka A^ano tafoEala", "text_ar": "يَحِقُّ عَلَيْكَ اَنْ تَفْعَلَ"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "ka*aA", "text_ar": "كَذَا"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "It is necessary for thee"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "as suitable to the requirements of wisdom"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "justice"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "the like"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "], or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "incumbent on thee,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "just"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "proper"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "right for thee, that thou shouldst do such a thing."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA.) [Thus one says,]"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AlHaqiyqapu maA yaHiq~u Ealayoka", "text_ar": "الحَقِيقَةُ مَا يَحِقُّ عَلَيْكَ"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^ano taHomiyahu", "text_ar": "اَنْ تَحْمِيَهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "The"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Hqyqp", "text_ar": "حقيقة"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "is that which it is necessary for thee"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "&c., or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "that which it behooveth thee, that thou shouldst defend it,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "protect it"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (S, * K.) Accord. to Sh, the Arabs said,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Haq~a EalaY~a A^ano", "text_ar": "حَقَّ عَلَىَّ اَنْ"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^afoEala *`lika", "text_ar": "اَفْعَلَ ذٰلِكَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Huq~a", "text_ar": "حُقَّ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": but accord. to Fr, when you say"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Haq~a", "text_ar": "حَقَّ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", you say"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Ealayoka", "text_ar": "عَلَيْكَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "; and when you say"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Huq~a", "text_ar": "حُقَّ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", you say"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "laka", "text_ar": "لَكَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (TA.) [Accordingly] one says,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Huq~a laka A^ano tafoEala *aA", "text_ar": "حُقَّ لَكَ اَنْ تَفْعَلَ ذَا"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Huqiqota A^ano tafoEalahu", "text_ar": "حُقِقْتَ اَنْ تَفْعَلَهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": both mean the same: (Ks, S, K:) [i. e., each has one, or the other, or both, of the meanings next following:] or the former means"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "It was,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or, emphatically,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "is, rendered"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "H~q~", "text_ar": "حّقّ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "suitable to the requirements of wisdom"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "justice"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "&c.]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "for thee,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "necessary for thee,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "incumbent on thee,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "just"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "proper"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "right for thee,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "it behooved"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "behooves thee,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "that thou shouldst do,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "to do, this,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "that:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and [the latter, or]"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Huqiqota biA^ano", "text_ar": "حُقِقْتَ بِاَنْ"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "tafoEala", "text_ar": "تَفْعَلَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ","}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Thou wast,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or, emphatically,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "art, rendered"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Haqiyq", "text_ar": "حَقِيق"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "adapted, disposed, apt, meet, suited, suitable, fitted, fit, proper, competent,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "worthy,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "that thou shouldst do,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "to do, this,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "that"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]: (A, TA:) and in like manner,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Huq~ato", "text_ar": "حُقَّتْ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "signifies in the Kur lxxxiv. 2 and 5: (Bd, Jel: *) or"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Huqiqota", "text_ar": "حُقِقْتَ"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "biA^ano tafoEala", "text_ar": "بِاَنْ تَفْعَلَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "may mean"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "thou wast,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "art, known by the testimony of thy circumstances to be"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Haqiyq", "text_ar": "حَقِيق"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "&c. (A, TA.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "maA kaAna yaHuq~uka A^ano tafoEalahu", "text_ar": "مَا كَانَ يَحُقُّكَ اَنْ تَفْعَلَهُ"}, {"kind": "page_break", "n": 606}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[virtually] means the same as"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "maA Huq~a laka", "text_ar": "مَا حُقَّ لَكَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[best rendered in this case"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "It did not behoove thee to do it"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (TA.) One says also,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Haq~a A^ano tafoEala", "text_ar": "حَقَّ اَنْ تَفْعَلَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "It was,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or, emphatically,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "is, necessary"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "&c."}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "that thou shouldst do"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "to do"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "such a thing]: but they did not say,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Haqaqota A^ano tafoEala", "text_ar": "حَقَقْتَ اَنْ تَفْعَلَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (Fr, TA.) ―         -b2-  But"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Haq~a EalaY~a A^ano tafoEala ka*aA", "text_ar": "حَقَّ عَلَىَّ اَنْ تَفْعَلَ كَذَا"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "means"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Thy doing so distressed,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "hath distressed,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "afflicted, me;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or, emphatically,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "distresses,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "afflicts, me;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "like"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Eaz~a EalaY~a", "text_ar": "عَزَّ عَلَىَّ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (S and K and TA in art."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Ez", "text_ar": "عز"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ".) And in like manner,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Haq~a A^an~aka *aAhibN", "text_ar": "حَقَّ اَنَّكَ ذَاهِبٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[or"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Haq~a maA A^an~aka *aAhibN", "text_ar": "حَقَّ مَا اَنَّكَ ذَاهِبٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "] means"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Eaz~a maA A^an~aka *aAhibN", "text_ar": "عَزَّ مَا اَنَّكَ ذَاهِبٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "It is distressing to me that thou art going away"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (TA in art."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Ez", "text_ar": "عز"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ".) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "laHaq~a maA", "text_ar": "لَحَقَّ مَا"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "is used in the same manner as"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "laEaz~a maA", "text_ar": "لَعَزَّ مَا"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", q. v. (A and TA in art."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Ez", "text_ar": "عز"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ".) You say also,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Haq~ati AlHaAjapu", "text_ar": "حَقَّتِ الحَاجَةُ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Want befell,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "betided,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "happened, and was severe,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "distressing:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Msb, TA:) [which is said to be] from the phrase,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Haq~ati", "text_ar": "حَقَّتِ"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AlqiyaAmapu", "text_ar": "القِيَامَةُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", aor."}, {"kind": "text", "text": ","}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "The resurrection included,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "shall include, within its sphere"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "all"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "the created beings."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Msb.)       -A2-"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Haq~ato", "text_ar": "حَقَّتْ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", aor."}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (K,) inf. n."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Hiq~apN", "text_ar": "حِقَّةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, * Msb, K,) and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Hiq~N", "text_ar": "حِقٌّ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (K,) or, accord. to ISd, it should rather be"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "HaqaAqapN", "text_ar": "حَقَاقَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "HuquwqapN", "text_ar": "حُقُوقَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", because"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Hiq~apN", "text_ar": "حِقَّةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "is used as an epithet, [as will be seen below,] and the inf. n. in a case like this, by rule, should differ from the epithet, (TA,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "She"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(a camel)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "became a"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Hiq~", "text_ar": "حِقّ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", or"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Hiq~ap", "text_ar": "حِقَّة"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "; i. e.,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "entered the fourth year:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(K:) and ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^aHaq~a", "text_ar": "اَحَقَّ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", inf. n."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A_iHoqaAqN", "text_ar": "اـِحْقَاقٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ","}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "he"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(a camel)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "became a"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Hiq~", "text_ar": "حِقّ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": because, so they say, he is then fit to be laden: (Msb:) and ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AHq~t", "text_ar": "احقّت", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "she"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(a young camel)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "completed three years;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Aboo-Málik, K;)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "became a"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Hiq~ap", "text_ar": "حِقَّة"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "; (Ibn-'Abbád, K;) like"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Haq~ato", "text_ar": "حَقَّتْ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (TA.) You say,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "huwa Haq~N bay~inu AlHiq~api", "text_ar": "هُوَ حَقٌّ بَيِّنُ الحِقَّةِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He is a"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Hq~", "text_ar": "حقّ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ","}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "bearing evidence of being such"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]: (S:) and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "hiYa Hiq~N", "text_ar": "هِىَ حِقٌّ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(K) and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Hiq~apN", "text_ar": "حِقَّةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Msb, K)"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "bay~inapu", "text_ar": "بَيِّنَةُ"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AlHiq~api", "text_ar": "الحِقَّةِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "she is a"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Hq~", "text_ar": "حقّ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Hq~p", "text_ar": "حقّة"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ","}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "bearing evidence"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "&c.]: (Msb:) [a phrase] to which a parallel is scarcely known, (Msb,) or to which there is no parallel (K) except"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^asadN bay~inu AlA^asadi", "text_ar": "اَسَدٌ بَيِّنُ الاَسَدِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[a lion bearing evidence of being like a lion in boldness]. (TA.) ―         -b2-"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Hiq~N", "text_ar": "حِقٌّ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[as inf. n. of"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Haq~ato", "text_ar": "حَقَّتْ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "] also signifies A she-camel's"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "overpassing the days"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "corresponding to those"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "in which she was covered"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "in the preceding year"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]: (K:) or her"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "completing"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "the time of"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "her pregnancy;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "as also ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AisotiHoqaAqN", "text_ar": "اِسْتِحْقَاقٌ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (TA.) ―         -b3-  And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Haq~ato", "text_ar": "حَقَّتْ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AHq~t", "text_ar": "احقّت", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AstHq~t", "text_ar": "استحقّت", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "She"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(a camel)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "became fat."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA. [See also 8, last signification.])       -A3-"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Haq~ahu", "text_ar": "حَقَّهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (K,) aor."}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", inf. n."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Haq~N", "text_ar": "حَقٌّ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (TA,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "it, rendered it"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "suitable to the requirements of wisdom, justice, rightness, truth,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "reality"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "fact;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "to the exigencies of the case;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(see the first of the significations in this art.;) or]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "necessary, requisite,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "unavoidable; binding, obligatory, incumbent,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "due;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "just, proper,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "right;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "syn."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^awojabahu", "text_ar": "اَوْجَبَهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "; (K;) [whence"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Huq~a laka A^ano tafoEala *aA", "text_ar": "حُقَّ لَكَ اَنْ تَفْعَلَ ذَا"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", explained above;] as also ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Hq~qhu", "text_ar": "حقّقهُ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(K) and ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AHq~hu", "text_ar": "احقّهُ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "; (S, K;) which last some explain by"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Say~arahu Haq~FA", "text_ar": "صَيَّرَهُ حَقًّا"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[meaning as above; or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "he rendered it true;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "] or"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Sy~rh Hq~FA laA $ak~a fiyhi", "text_ar": "صيّره حقًّا لَا شَكَّ فِيهِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "he rendered it true, so that there was no doubt respecting it"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]; as also"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Haq~ahu", "text_ar": "حَقَّهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", inf. n."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Haq~N", "text_ar": "حَقٌّ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Haq~ahu", "text_ar": "حَقَّهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "signifies also"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "he established it so that it became true and undoubted in his estimation:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA:) or"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Haq~ahu", "text_ar": "حَقَّهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "signifies, (S, Msb,) or signifies also, (K,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "he assured,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "certified, himself of it; he ascertained it; he was,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "became, sure,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "certain, of it;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(A 'Obeyd, S, Msb, * K; *) and so ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "tHq~qh", "text_ar": "تحقّقه", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(A 'Obeyd, S, K) and ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AHq~hu", "text_ar": "احقّهُ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": (S, Msb: *) or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "he pronounced it,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "held"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "believed it, to be established as a necessary truth"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "fact;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "as also ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AHq~hu", "text_ar": "احقّهُ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": and ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Hq~qhu", "text_ar": "حقّقهُ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "has a similar, but intensive, signification: (Msb:) or ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AHq~hu", "text_ar": "احقّهُ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "signifies"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "he established it as true;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "he judged,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "decided, it to be so:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA: ["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "contr. of"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^aboTalahu", "text_ar": "اَبْطَلَهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": see an ex., from the Kur viii., voce"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^aboTala", "text_ar": "اَبْطَلَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ":]) and ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Hq~qhu", "text_ar": "حقّقهُ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", inf. n."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "taHoqiyqN", "text_ar": "تَحْقِيقٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", signifies"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Sad~aqahu", "text_ar": "صَدَّقَهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[as meaning"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "he verified it,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "proved it to be true"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "veritable;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "he found it to be true"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "veritable;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "both of which significations are of very frequent occurrence]; (S, K;) as also"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Haq~ahu", "text_ar": "حَقَّهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", inf. n."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Haq~N", "text_ar": "حَقٌّ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": and accord. to IDrd, ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Hq~qhu", "text_ar": "حقّقهُ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "signifies [also]"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Sad~aqa qaAy^ilahu", "text_ar": "صَدَّقَ قَايِلَهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "he proved,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "found,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "pronounced, the sayer of it to be ture"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]: and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Hq~q", "text_ar": "حقّق"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "is also said to signify"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "he said,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "“"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "This thing is the truth;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "” like"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Sad~aqa", "text_ar": "صَدَّقَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (TA.) You say,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Haqaqotu Ealayohi AlqaDaA='a", "text_ar": "حَقَقْتُ عَلَيْهِ القَضَا=ءَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", aor."}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", inf. n."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Haq~N", "text_ar": "حَقٌّ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ","}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "I necessitated the sentence"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "as suitable to the requirements of justice"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "to take effect upon him;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "necessitated"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "as suitable"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "&c.]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "the taking effect of the sentence upon him;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "syn."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^awojabotuhu", "text_ar": "اَوْجَبْتُهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "; as also ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^aHoqaqotuhu", "text_ar": "اَحْقَقْتُهُ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", inf. n."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A_iHoqaAqN", "text_ar": "اـِحْقَاقٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (TA.) And ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^uHiq~a", "text_ar": "اُحِقَّ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Ealayoka AlqaDaA='u", "text_ar": "عَلَيْكَ القَضَا=ءُ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "The sentence was,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or, emphatically,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "is, necessitated"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "as suitable to the requirements of justice"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "to take effect upon thee;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "syn."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^uvobita", "text_ar": "اُثْبِتَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (TA.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Haqaqotu Ha*arahu", "text_ar": "حَقَقْتُ حَذَرَهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (S, K,) or"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Hi*orahu", "text_ar": "حِذْرَهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (so in one copy of the S,) aor. and inf. n. as above, (S,) ["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "I rendered his caution,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "fear, necessary;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "justified it;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "meaning]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "I did that of which he was cautious,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "that which he feared;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, K;) as also"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "H*rh", "text_ar": "حذره"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^aHoqaqotu", "text_ar": "اَحْقَقْتُ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": (S:) or, accord. to Az, the latter only is right. (TA.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Haqaqotu Zan~ahu", "text_ar": "حَقَقْتُ ظَنَّهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "; (Ks, TA;) and ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Haq~aqotuhu", "text_ar": "حَقَّقْتُهُ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (Ks, S, TA,) inf. n."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "taHoqiyqN", "text_ar": "تَحْقِيقٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": (S:) both signify the same; (Ks, TA;) i. e."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Sad~aqotu", "text_ar": "صَدَّقْتُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "; (S;) which means"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "I found his opinion to be true;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Ksh and Bd and Jel, in xxxiv. 19;) or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "proved it to be true:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Ksh, ibid.:) and so"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "qawolahu", "text_ar": "قَوْلَهُ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "his saying:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S:) and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "taHoqiyqN", "text_ar": "تَحْقِيقٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "signifies [also] the"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "strengthening,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "confirming,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "a saying; or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "making"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "it"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "strong,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "firm."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(KL.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^anaA", "text_ar": "اَنَا"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^aHaq~u lakumo h`*aA Alxabara", "text_ar": "اَحَقُّ لَكُمْ هٰذَا الخَبَرَ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "I will know,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "ascertain, the truth,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "real nature, of this piece of news"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "information, for you."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^aZun~uhu wa laA", "text_ar": "اَظُنُّهُ وَ لَا"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^aHuq~uhu", "text_ar": "اَحُقُّهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "I think it, but I do not know the truth of it,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "am not certain of it"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (T in art."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A_iy~aA", "text_ar": "اـِيَّا"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "; &c.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Haqaqotu AlEuqodapa", "text_ar": "حَقَقْتُ العُقْدَةَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", [written in the TA without any syll. signs, so that it may be either thus or ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Haq~aqotuhu", "text_ar": "حَقَّقْتُهُ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "; but it is most probably the former, as the quasi-pass. is not"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "tHq~qt", "text_ar": "تحقّقت"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", but"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AnHq~t", "text_ar": "انحقّت"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": it signifies lit."}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "I made the knot right,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "sure;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "meaning] (tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "I tied,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "made fast,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "tightened, the knot;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Ibn-'Abbád, TA;) or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "I tied,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "tightened, firmly the knot."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(A, TA.)  ―         -b2-  ["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "it, rendered him"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Haqiyq", "text_ar": "حَقِيق"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", i. e."}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "adapted, disposed, apt, meet, suited, suitable, fitted, fit, proper,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "worthy,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "to do a thing &c.; whence"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Huqiqota A^ano tafoEalahu", "text_ar": "حُقِقْتَ اَنْ تَفْعَلَهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", or"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "biA^ano tafoEala", "text_ar": "بِاَنْ تَفْعَلَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", explained above. ―         -b3-"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "It was necessary for him,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "incumbent on him,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "just"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "proper"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "right for him,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "it behooved him,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "to do a thing &c.; whence"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "maA", "text_ar": "مَا"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "kaAna yaHuq~uka A^ano tafoEalahu", "text_ar": "كَانَ يَحُقُّكَ اَنْ تَفْعَلَهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", explained above.] ―         -b4-  Also, (S, K,) aor."}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (K,) inf. n."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Haq~N", "text_ar": "حَقٌّ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (TA,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He overcame him in disputing,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "contending, for a right,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "due;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, K, * TA;) and so ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AHq~hu", "text_ar": "احقّهُ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (K,) inf. n."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A_iHoqaAqN", "text_ar": "اـِحْقَاقٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", mentioned by Az on the authority of Ks, but, he adds, disallowed by A 'Obeyd. (TA.) See 3. ―         -b5-  Also"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(a man)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "came to him,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "namely, another man; (A 'Obeyd, S, K;) and so ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AHq~hu", "text_ar": "احقّهُ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (A 'Obeyd, S.) [Hence, app.,]"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Haq~atoniY Al$~amosu", "text_ar": "حَقَّتْنِى الشَّمْسُ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "The sun reached me."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "laA yHq~u maA", "text_ar": "لَا يحقُّ مَا"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "fiY h`*aA AlwiEaA='i riTolFA", "text_ar": "فِى هٰذَا الوِعَا=ءِ رِطْلًا"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[app."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "yaHuq~u", "text_ar": "يَحُقُّ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "What is in this receptacle"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "does not reach,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "amount, to a pound;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "i. e.,]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "does not weigh a pound."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA.)       -A4-"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Haq~a", "text_ar": "حَقَّ"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AlT~ariyqa", "text_ar": "الطَّرِيقَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (K,) aor."}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (TA,) inf. n."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Haq~N", "text_ar": "حَقٌّ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (TK,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He went upon the"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "HaAq~", "text_ar": "حَاقّ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "of the road;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(K;) i. e."}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "the middle of it:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "the doing of which is forbidden, in a trad., to women. (TA.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Haq~a fulaAnFA", "text_ar": "حَقَّ فُلَانًا"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (K,) aor. and inf. n. as above, (TA,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He beat,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "struck, such a one in,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "upon, the"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "HAq~", "text_ar": "حاقّ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "of his head;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(K;) i. e."}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "the middle of it:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA:) or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "in,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "upon, the"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Huq~", "text_ar": "حُقّ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "of his"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "katif", "text_ar": "كَتِف"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "; i. e."}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "the small hollow upon the head of his shoulder-blade:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(K:) or, as some say,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "the head of the upper arm, in which is the"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "waAbilap", "text_ar": "وَابِلَة"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (TA.)"}], "source_r